Package: ggsmatr
Title: Ggsmatr
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Mario A.", "Sandoval-Molina", , "sandoval.m@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8536-6006"))
Description: The "ggsmatr" provides a simple and efficient way to visualize the coefficients of the (Standardized) Major Axis Estimation fit from the "smatr" package using ggplot2. With just a few lines of code, users can create clear and customizable scatterplots that highlight the relationships between variables. This package is a valuable tool for researchers and data analysts looking to explore and communicate their data in a visually appealing way.
